results.name: Start with n and repeatedly apply the powerback map of A133048. Sequence gives number of steps to the point where the next number would be one that has appeared before.
comment: It is conjectured that every number eventually reaches a fixed point (see A131571) or the cycle of length 2 given by (175 <-> 78125).
results.author: _J. H. Conway_ and _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jan 01 2008
